<figureCitation id="13392A41FF9BB075FF614105FEF5FCD4" box="[201,269,803,827]" captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="10.[194,278,1161,1183]" captionTargetBox="[192,1441,194,1134]" captionTargetId="figure-276@10.[192,1441,194,1134]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="Figure 4. Phycitiplex peralta, female, holotype. Santa Vera Cruz, La Rioja, Argentina. Lateral view of entire insect." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5170159" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5170159/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
